name: symNMF
description: This repository contains the implementation of symmetric Non-negative Matrix Factorization (symNMF) algorithms. The project is primarily written in C and Python, with supporting Makefiles for build configuration. It includes tools and libraries for performing matrix factorization, demonstrating applications in data analysis and machine learning.

name: Clustering-Spasial-untuk-Pemetaan-Kebun-Sekitar-Gunung-Dempo-Pasca-Erupsi-dengan-K-Means
description: Proyek ini memetakan dampak erupsi Gunung Dempo 2023 di Pagar Alam menggunakan K-Means Clustering. Data citra satelit diolah dengan Normalized Burn Ratio (NBR) untuk mengidentifikasi area terdampak dan tidak terdampak. Pengolahan menggunakan QGIS dan Python, dengan evaluasi Davies-Bouldin Score.

name: Kaggle-Credit-Risk-Assessment
description: This project explores credit risk assessment using three models: Random Forest, Self-Organizing Maps (SOM), and a hybrid approach combining both.
